Commentary Text: Pathirana to Marco Jansen, out Washington Sundar Run Out!! A run-out to end the innings, SRH finish with 134, slower ball from Pathirana, Jansen swung and missed - they were always going for a bye, but MS was ready, took aim and broke the stumps, catching Washington Sundar just short of his ground. Washington Sundar run out (Dhoni) 9(6) [4s-1]

Gaikwad run out (Umran Malik) 35(30) [4s-2]
